                                                  <a name="post315" href="/web/20110312102621/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/showthread.php/71-Highway-7-8-Transportation-Corridor-Planning-amp-Class-EA-Study?p=315#post315" class="postcounter">#3</a><a id="postcount315" name="3"></a>
                                          
                                          
                                          
